data.description: Welcome to your new home, where style meets functionality! This stunning 4 bed, 2 bath home is designed with entertaining in mind. With an open floor plan that effortlessly connects the living room and large kitchen, this home is perfect for hosting friends and family. The kitchen is a chef's dream come true, with ample storage and countertop space that make meal preparation a breeze. With an abundance of natural light and high ceilings, the living and dining areas are perfect for relaxing and spending time with loved ones. The oversized corner lot offers plenty of space for outdoor activities, and the private saltwater pool provides the perfect spot for a refreshing dip on a hot summer day. This home offers a split floor plan with 3 spacious bedrooms on one side of the home and the primary retreat on the other side. The primary retreat features a spa-like ensuite bathroom with soaking tub, dual vanities with sinks, and a large walk-in closet. This home also boasts a new roof, installed in 2023, ensuring years of worry-free living. Located in a prime location, this home is just minutes away from schools, shopping centers, and dining options. Sabal Harbour offers many amenities with no CDD fees, low HOA fees, community pool, playground, tennis and basketball courts. If you're looking for a home that combines comfort, style, and functionality, look no further! This home is an entertainer's dream, and it's ready for you to make it your own.
